# Viewing Pictures

Read this section for information on playback zoom and multi-frame playback.

Use the rear command dial to go from full-frame playback to playback zoom or multi-frame playback.

!Rear Command Dial

- **Full-frame playback**

  !Full-frame Playback

- **Playback zoom**

  - Medium zoom
    !Medium Zoom
  - Maximum zoom
    !Maximum Zoom

- **Multi-frame playback**

  - Nine-frame view
    !Nine-frame View
  - Hundred-frame view
    !Hundred-frame View
